{"tid":1344082,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(勿認真純講笑)提倡搞翻個廢老物資站","createTime":"2019-07-21T20:25:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T20:25:47.000Z","uid":44804,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f443c2a6e557da1e62bd4e3ff7a7a1d823687793","tid":1344082,"uid":44804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:25:47.000Z","msg":"其實啲老野又多病又骨質疏鬆(仲咁大火氣)<br />\n軟骨頭碰硬骨頭 或者激兩激都入得ICU<br />\n本身都半隻腳叉入棺材<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解唔搞翻個廢老物資站支援下佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時啲<span style=\"color: maroon;\">食水</span>轉做啲<span style=\"color: blue;\">珍珠奶茶,芝麻糊,可樂</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">食物</span>就整啲<span style=\"color: blue;\">炸薯條,豬油撈飯</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(多鹽多油又好食又多營養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n跟住<span style=\"color: maroon;\">洗眼水同生理鹽水</span>就係<span style=\"color: blue;\">驅風油啊白花油同保濟丸</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再黎就係<span style=\"color: maroon;\">頭盔同雨遮(藤條)</span>就係<span style=\"color: blue;\">拐杖同輪椅</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再加啲<span style=\"color: maroon;\">助慶站台</span> 揾屯門公園果班大媽做陪唱<br />\n娜娜做嘉賓 現場搞翻個抽獎<br />\n<br />\n頭獎: 某某老人院嘅入院名額<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二獎: 醫療券<br />\n三獎: 豪華棺材加專業破地獄體驗券一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾貼心~fit曬! 掂曬!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">利申:朋友諗出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔關我事 <br />\n<br />\n望君一笑 舒解壓力</span>"}]}